org.testng
Class Assert

java.lang.Object
  org.testng.Assert

public class Assert
extends java.lang.Object

Assertion tool class. Presents assertion methods with a more natural parameter order. The order is always actualValue, expectedValue [, message].

Author:
Alexandru Popescu
